---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/paths';
---

<PageLayout title="Mission Statement" description="Learn about the Los Angeles Bicycle Advisory Committee, its mission, and history since 1973.">
  <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">Founded in 1973</p>

  <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-4 my-6 text-text-muted italic">
    The purpose of the BAC is to act in an advisory capacity to the Mayor, City Council Members, and the various agencies of the government of the City of Los Angeles in the encouragement and facilitation of the use of the bicycle as regular means of transportation and recreation.
    <footer class="mt-2 text-sm not-italic font-medium">&mdash; BAC Charter</footer>
  </blockquote>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">What We Do</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    The Los Angeles Bicycle Advisory Committee (LABAC) advises the Mayor, City Council, and City departments on policies, programs, and projects that affect bicycle transportation in the City of Los Angeles.
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
    <li>Review and comment on bicycle-related projects and plans</li>
    <li>Advise on the City's Bicycle Plan and Mobility Plan 2035</li>
    <li>Provide a public forum for bicycle transportation issues</li>
    <li>Collaborate with LADOT, Metro, and other agencies</li>
    <li>Advocate for safe and accessible cycling infrastructure</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Meeting Schedule</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    LABAC meets the first Tuesday of every even month (February, April, June, August, October, December) at 7 PM at the Hollywood Neighborhood City Hall Community Room, 6501 Fountain Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90028.
  </p>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    Sub-committees meet during odd months at various locations.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Key Documents</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-2">
    <li><a href={url('/documents/labac/charter.pdf')} class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LABAC Charter</a></li>
    <li><a href={url('/documents/labac/strategic-plan-2023.pdf')} class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Strategic Plan 2023</a></li>
    <li><a href={url('/documents/labac/resource-guide.pdf')} class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bicycling Resource Guide A-to-Z</a></li>
  </ul>
</PageLayout>
